item.description:
This lovely park is tucked away on the South Shore. I pleasantly surprised the first time I visited. Below is a link with a full description.

http://www.thetrustee...

Please plan for a 2 hour hike. The pace will be moderate, and led by Kate. Thanks Kate!

Please bring plenty of water and snacks for you and your pets.
item.how_to_find_us: Kate will be in a blue Jeep Cherokee. I drive a green Chevy Silverado
